At present, when handling an unsupported operation, the federated store returns an internal server error with status code 500. There is no descriptive error message. To correct this, the following code could be removed from the FederatedStore class:
```java
    @Override
    protected Object doUnhandledOperation(final Operation operation,
                                          final Context context) {
        throw new UnsupportedOperationException();
    }
```
