Each operation can be given a score and when an operation chain is executed the scores for each operation is summed. The total score for the operation chain is then compared against an allowed maximum score for the given user.

This works well for normal operations. Named Operations and potentially other operations in the future may need to have a variable score depending on how it is configured. So it would be useful to have another interface:

